<%= render "shared/header" %>
<main class="bg-slate-50 w-full flex flex-col items-center justify-center">
  <!--Container for contents-->
  <div class="lg:w-3/5 md:w-4/5 pb-10">
    <h1 class="font-bold text-4xl py-10 text-center">Get ready to fly!</h1>  
    <p class="px-5 p-text pb-5">
    Thank you<%if notice.present?%>, <%= notice %>,<%end%> for requesting to visit Sun City Aviation Academy.  We're excited to meet you and can't wait to share our passion for flying with you.
    A member of our team will be in touch shortly. You can also give us a call at <%=link_to "1-754-423-2159", "tel:1-754-423-2159" %> or email us at <%= mail_to 'info@suncityaviation.com', class: "text-yellow-600 hover:underline"%>
    </p>
    <p class="px-5 p-text pb-5 italic text-slate-700 text-sm">
    NOTE: Please keep an eye on your inbox.  We will be sending an email to you.  Please check your junk/spam folders if you do not receive anything from us.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row">
    <div class="lg:w-1/2 lg:px-10">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-2xl py-10 text-center">What to Expect From Sun City Aviation Academy</h2>
      <p class="p-text px-5">
        At Sun City Aviation Academy, we are committed to providing our customers with exceptional service and support at every step of their journey. From the moment you walk through our doors, you can expect a friendly and knowledgeable staff who will help guide you through the flight training process and answer any questions you may have. We pride ourselves on maintaining a fleet of well maintained and reliable aircraft. Our commitment to safety is unwavering, and we maintain rigorous training standards for our pilots and staff. Whether you are a seasoned pilot or a beginner, we look forward to helping you achieve your goals and experience the thrill of flight. Thank you for choosing Sun City Aviation Academy!
      </p>
      <div class="pt-10 flex flex-row gap-3 justify-center">
        <%= link_to pilot_courses_path do %>
          <div class="btn-primary mb-10">
            VIEW PROGRAMS
          </div>
        <% end %>

        <%= link_to root_path do %>
          <div class="btn-primary mb-10">
            HOME PAGE
          </div>
        <% end %>
      </div>

    </div>
    
    <div class="lg:w-1/2">
      <%= image_tag "sun-city-miami-from-plane.webp", class: "lg:w-3/4", alt: "fly over South Florida Miami"%>
    </div>
  </div>

</main>

<%= render "shared/footer"%>